==Daily==
===Searching for signal...===
{{Messages|text=
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Searching for signal...
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Unstable Signal
:'''Phainon:''' Partner, by the time you see this message, I should have already started my journey to my final destination.
:'''Phainon:''' Unfortunately, I still haven't read most of the books I bought that time at the Grove.
:'''Phainon:''' Among them, there's one named "Legend of Celestial Skies." The plot is full of twists and turns, I strongly recommend it.
:'''Phainon:''' I read about how the protagonist conquered all obstacles, and was about to fight the last monster. And then, I ran out of time.
:'''Phainon:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 23 Phainon 04.png|80px]]
:'''Phainon:''' I heard that the ending of that story is beyond expectations.
:'''Phainon:''' When you have the time, read it for me.
:'''Phainon:''' After we find a way to defeat the Irontomb, let's bid farewell under the stars you talked about.
:'''Phainon:''' When that time comes, please tell me how it ends.
:'''Phainon:''' When I was reading that book, I even carved a wooden sculpture of the hero in the story.
:'''Phainon:''' It's really cool, you'll love it. I'll give it to you the next time we meet!
:'''Phainon:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 23 Phainon 02.png|80px]]
:{Choice} Dawn will rise!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' My friend, we see the light that you've ignited for the world.
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Dawn will rise!
:{Choice} When can we meet again?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Will we see each other again?
:{Choice} The story ends with...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I read it for you, it's a happy ending!
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Message failed to send.
:{{DIcon|Warning}} The user you're trying to reach is currently out of the service area. Please try again later.
}}
