===Partner!===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Phainon:''' Partner!
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend is typing...
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend is typing...
:{{DIcon|Warning}} Your friend is typing...
:{Choice} Good to see you!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Phainon? Good to see you again!
:{Choice} What's up?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What's up?
:{Choice} Don't leave me hanging
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Don't leave me hanging. What is it?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What's wrong?
:'''Phainon:''' Well... I've finally got some downtime, but I can't sit still, so I've been trying to keep myself busy
:'''Phainon:''' Aglaea, Lady Tribbie... they all have their own fields they're dedicated to
:'''Phainon:''' So on a whim, I wanted to try out some different jobs, learn some new abilities, and maybe discover some more hobbies!
:'''Phainon:''' I've tried being a chef, a locksmith, a haunted house actor, an outfit model, a dromas tamer, an auctioneer...
:'''Phainon:''' But none of them really felt like the right fit, you know?
:'''Phainon:''' Got any other suggestions for me, partner?
:{Choice} A pilot
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Like the blazing sun destined to rise&mdash;
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You should cruise through the sky!
:{Choice} Watercolor painter
::'''(Trailblazer):''' How about a watercolor painter? It would help you improve your sense of color
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sounds like a good challenge, right?
:{Choice} Dog trainer
::'''(Trailblazer):''' A dog trainer. I think you have a real talent for it
:'''Phainon:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 23 Phainon 01.png|80px]]
:'''Phainon:''' You've really given me an inspiration!
:'''Phainon:''' I should think outside the box and take on more challenges that will take me to the skies and back!
:'''Phainon:''' Like skydiving, for example. I'm not afraid of heights. I could probably go even higher
:'''Phainon:''' Also... how about becoming a pro athlete?
:'''Phainon:''' Based on my scores, I think I have a bit of a knack for it
:'''Phainon:''' [[File:Sticker PPG 23 Mem 03.png|80px]]
:'''Phainon:''' That sounds amazing!
:'''Phainon:''' I'm getting more and more excited just thinking about it!
:'''Phainon:''' I'm going to go try it out right now!
:'''Phainon:''' See you around!
}}
